---
const requirements = [
  "Minimum required credentials for integrations",
  "Only the tables/fields needed for workflow state and reconciliation",
  "A small test group of users/roles for validation"
];
---
<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16 reveal">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary dark:text-stone-50 mb-8">
    What we need access to (high level)
  </h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-8">
    {requirements.map(req => (
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start group">
        <iconify-icon class="text-amber-600 mt-0.5" icon="solar:check-circle-linear" stroke-width="1.5" width="18"></iconify-icon>
        <span class="text-sm text-primary dark:text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
          {req}
        </span>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
  <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-stone-500 font-medium">
    We don’t ask for broad access “just in case.”
  </p>
</section>